{"tid":1264797,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[未出已經最佳] 《Final Fantasy VII Remake》獲三項E3大獎 成19年最佳遊戲","createTime":"2019-06-29T00:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:59:56.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d16a01dfe09ced434df5eb5b223f69bcffa6c02","tid":1264797,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T00:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368600793410428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2368600793410428&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=9641b006\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368600793410428</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0chcbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0chcbm.jpg&h=890478cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【業界】《最終幻想7：重製版》獲三項E3大獎 成19年最佳遊戲<br />\n<br />\n  前天（6月26日）Game Critics Awards公佈了2019年E3各大獎項的提名名單之後，今天（6月28日）該機構發布了這批獲獎遊戲的名單。來自SQUARE ENIX的《最終幻想7：重製版》成為年度最佳展出獎，其他具體獎項獲獎名單如下：<br />\n<br />\n最佳展出獎－－－－－－最終幻想7重製版（Final Fantasy VII Remake）<br />\n最佳原創獎－－－－－－外部世界（The Outer Worlds）<br />\n最佳主機遊戲－－－－－最終幻想7重製版（Final Fantasy VII Remake）<br />\n最佳VR/AR遊戲－－－－Phantom: Covert Ops<br />\n最佳PC遊戲－－－－－－毀滅戰士：永恆（DOOM ETERNAL)<br />\n最佳硬件/外設－－－－－Xbox精英手柄2（Xbox Elite Wireless Controller Series 2)<br />\n最佳動作遊戲－－－－－毀滅戰士：永恆（DOOM ETERNAL)<br />\n最佳動作/冒險遊戲－－－看門狗：軍團（WATCH DOGS LEGION ）<br />\n最佳RPG遊戲－－－－－最終幻想7重製版（Final Fantasy VII Remake）<br />\n最佳競速遊戲－－－－－古惑狼賽車重製版《 Crash Team Racing Nitro-Fueled 》<br />\n最佳運動遊戲－－－－－實況足球2020《eFootball PES 2020》<br />\n最佳策略遊戲－－－－－疾速追殺Hex （John Wick Hex）<br />\n最佳家庭遊戲－－－－－路易的鬼屋3《Luigi Mansion 3》<br />\n最佳多人網絡遊戲－－－使命召喚：現代戰爭（Call of Duty: Modern Warfare）<br />\n最佳獨立遊戲－－－－－12分鐘 （12 Minutes）<br />\n最佳運營遊戲－－－－－命運2 （Destiny 2）<br />\n畫面特別推薦獎－－－－賽博朋客2077 （Cyberpunk 2077）<br />\n<br />\n  這其中最大的贏家當然就是包攬三大獎項的《最終幻想7重製版》，畢竟現場給出的演示已經足夠讓粉絲們耐心地等到明年遊戲正式上市，你認為呢？不過如果《賽博朋客2077》對外公開展示，說不定最佳展出獎花落誰家還不一定吧？<br />\n<br />\n-----"},{"pid":"7f1b4d3361820be08905890b82741c22fda75121","tid":1264797,"uid":122915,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"未出都拎獎<br />\n真係ON99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n展出獎都算數當合資格<br />\n屌你主機遊戲同RPG遊戲玩都未撚玩得都拎得獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0632cdf0c0bafd7b6e726c7ca1de468dc1d67ac0","tid":1264797,"uid":75050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7f1b4d3361820be08905890b82741c22fda75121","tid":1264797,"uid":122915,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"未出都拎獎<br />\n真係ON99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n展出獎都算數當合資格<br />\n屌你主機遊戲同RPG遊戲玩都未撚玩得都拎得獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:09:47.000Z","msg":"Cyberpunk 2077 仲要得個豬肉獎，屌你其他廠無比錢買獎我真係唔柒信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304701fd806664b9b5c4a6a197de0c13b33e5987","tid":1264797,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921557f45ce1cdf442dacec76e3c979ab5773266","tid":1264797,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cb954279e75e21896fe5a5a4f8118a44234f77","tid":1264797,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"20年發售既19年最佳遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0904c5ed6cfbc0711a47970dceeb14c833038c1","tid":1264797,"uid":75479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime